Board Prep Resources

Source: R/data.R
board_prep_df.Rd

Resources used by nephrology fellows in preparation for initial board certication in nephrology. This is a synthesized data set generated based on proportions of actual responses to measures in the 2025 ASN Nephrology Fellow Survey.

Usage

board_prep_df

Format

A data frame with 8 columns

  1. q6: Repondent medical school location, either "United States" or "Other country".

  2. q65_1: ASN Kidney Self-Assessment Program (KSAP) selected as a used resource ( = "No").

  3. q65_2: ASN Nephrology Self-Assessment Program (NephSAP) selected as a used resource ( = "No").

  4. q65_3: ASN Board Review Course & Update selected as a used resource ( = "No").

  5. q65_4: Oakstone/Brigham Intensive Review of Nephrology Course ( = "No").

  6. q65_5: Other board review course ( = "No").

  7. q65_6: Other resource(s) (please specify) ( = "No").

  8. q65_6_text: Free text response describing other resource(s) used.
